The [[Allmusic]] review awarded the album 4Â½ stars stating "Although not containing any real surprises, this swinging, straight-ahead music is quite enjoyable".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/live-in-tokyo-mw0000897318 Allmusic Review] accessed April 29, 2014</ref>

